#originalTopic=is-there-a-god
Consider how much of our DNA is shared by chimpanzees (about 97%). Consider cross-species transfer of viruses, bacteria, etc. whereby humans get malaria, hantavirus, dengue fever and other diseases.That by itself is sufficient to show that "Intelligent Design" is oxymoronic. As one of my Philosophy instructors often stated: "If God created the universe, he was an incompetent engineer."